{"submission_id":"sub_e1c5e8b4adf26146","run_id":"2026-06-21T20-11-51-798Z_3137823-bef50061_ingest_meeting-doc-186706","submitted_at":"2026-06-21T20:23:29.849Z","tool_args_sha256":"sha256:e1c5e8b4adf2614684d6695ff9612648a0e4d4030bfa08f5118a9bf8db2da61b","schema_version":2,"tool_args":{"source_id":"meeting_doc_186706","observation_kind":"claim","local_observation_id":"claim_oscar_dashboard","label":"OSCAR Dashboard Capabilities","raw_text":"OSCAR - Operations Security Console and Reporting: Centralized Dashboard – Aggregates alerts and incidents across LIRR locations. Trend Analysis – Identifies hotspots and recurring issues. Refined Monitoring – Helps reduce false positives and unnecessary calls for service. Resource Allocation – Guides smarter deployment of security assets and requests for service. Continuous Improvement – Provides feedback loop to strengthen alerts and response coordination.","payload":{"claim_text":"OSCAR (Operations Security Console and Reporting) is a centralized dashboard that aggregates alerts and incidents across LIRR locations, provides trend analysis to identify hotspots and recurring issues, refines monitoring to reduce false positives and unnecessary calls for service, guides smarter deployment of security assets, and provides a feedback loop to strengthen alerts and response coordination."},"evidence_refs":[{"source_id":"meeting_doc_186706","evidence_id":"meeting_doc_186706#p010_c0003","source_path":"raw/sources/meeting_doc_186706/blocks.jsonl","page_number":10,"block_id":"p010_c0003","text_sha256":"sha256:12e8c9c02fae23813793c91bb4f1eb5a5d12f8263890ebef5db58b92440a71c8","text_source":"raw_text","role":"claim"}]},"validation":{"state":"accepted","issues":[]}}
{"submission_id":"sub_da4a02dbf9d1d882","run_id":"2026-06-21T20-11-51-798Z_3137823-bef50061_ingest_meeting-doc-186706","submitted_at":"2026-06-21T20:23:38.464Z","tool_args_sha256":"sha256:da4a02dbf9d1d882fb4d8eb4b9080ed8fe1f8e0147fb52095233a81bcfcfa1b9","schema_version":2,"tool_args":{"source_id":"meeting_doc_186706","observation_kind":"claim","local_observation_id":"claim_lirr_system_scale","label":"LIRR System Scale","raw_text":"The LIRR spans 126 stations, 56 yards, and over 700 miles of track.","payload":{"claim_text":"The LIRR spans 126 stations, 56 yards, and over 700 miles of track."},"evidence_refs":[{"source_id":"meeting_doc_186706","evidence_id":"meeting_doc_186706#p008_c0004","source_path":"raw/sources/meeting_doc_186706/blocks.jsonl","page_number":8,"block_id":"p008_c0004","text_sha256":"sha256:1a5118b022a1e4da75277bf14235555d566c75a1ad68e8fe2a8f3ab83989ebd4","text_source":"raw_text","role":"claim"}]},"validation":{"state":"accepted","issues":[]}}
{"submission_id":"sub_cc8e051742b2279f","run_id":"2026-06-21T20-11-51-798Z_3137823-bef50061_ingest_meeting-doc-186706","submitted_at":"2026-06-21T20:23:47.980Z","tool_args_sha256":"sha256:cc8e051742b2279f20699236ead2616d59eaac5859bdafde9a6d92d349e5806e","schema_version":2,"tool_args":{"source_id":"meeting_doc_186706","observation_kind":"claim","local_observation_id":"claim_case_study_storage_yard_theft","label":"Video Monitoring Case Study - Storage Yard Theft Prevention","raw_text":"Alert received for after-hours movement at a storage yard. Video showed two individuals trespassing in a restricted area. LIRR Command Center personnel notified MTA Police Department of suspicious activity. MTAPD apprehended and arrested three individuals for the theft. The van used by the individuals was involved in a previous incident.","payload":{"claim_text":"Alert received for after-hours movement at a storage yard. Video showed two individuals trespassing in a restricted area. LIRR Command Center personnel notified MTA Police Department of suspicious activity. MTAPD apprehended and arrested three individuals for the theft. The van used by the individuals was involved in a previous incident."},"evidence_refs":[{"source_id":"meeting_doc_186706","evidence_id":"meeting_doc_186706#p011_c0003","source_path":"raw/sources/meeting_doc_186706/blocks.jsonl","page_number":11,"block_id":"p011_c0003","text_sha256":"sha256:f86db29910d3eb9d9f0a643539b7e13470eea51895990a945763ef978c765cfe","text_source":"raw_text","role":"case_study"}]},"validation":{"state":"accepted","issues":[]}}
{"submission_id":"sub_1bb323e842d34830","run_id":"2026-06-21T20-11-51-798Z_3137823-bef50061_ingest_meeting-doc-186706","submitted_at":"2026-06-21T20:23:59.472Z","tool_args_sha256":"sha256:1bb323e842d348300eabe412f3b2079067ca3f07b6e7a294dfb4fc4577875ee4","schema_version":2,"tool_args":{"source_id":"meeting_doc_186706","observation_kind":"claim","local_observation_id":"claim_case_study_property_theft_prevention","label":"Video Monitoring Case Study - Property Theft Prevention","raw_text":"LIRR Command Center personnel, through proactive video monitoring, identified unusual activity in a storage yard. Video showed an individual trespassing in a restricted area. Command personnel promptly notified MTA Police Department. MTAPD responded and prevented the individual from removing property from the yard.","payload":{"claim_text":"LIRR Command Center personnel, through proactive video monitoring, identified unusual activity in a storage yard. Video showed an individual trespassing in a restricted area. Command personnel promptly notified MTA Police Department. MTAPD responded and prevented the individual from removing property from the yard."},"evidence_refs":[{"source_id":"meeting_doc_186706","evidence_id":"meeting_doc_186706#p012_c0003","source_path":"raw/sources/meeting_doc_186706/blocks.jsonl","page_number":12,"block_id":"p012_c0003","text_sha256":"sha256:6663fa334aa3e0cad466281e24ee59abd610e092e0a928496d062d46d4f8ec2e","text_source":"raw_text","role":"case_study"}]},"validation":{"state":"accepted","issues":[]}}
{"submission_id":"sub_ecfd1b1264e6640c","run_id":"2026-06-21T20-11-51-798Z_3137823-bef50061_ingest_meeting-doc-186706","submitted_at":"2026-06-21T20:24:11.267Z","tool_args_sha256":"sha256:ecfd1b1264e6640cdf78ef90f608b4eb3976b679a6c1be2454b7875df6551f57","schema_version":2,"tool_args":{"source_id":"meeting_doc_186706","observation_kind":"claim","local_observation_id":"claim_video_analysis_impact","label":"Impact of Video Analysis Program","raw_text":"Coordinated, consistent incident handling. Intelligent deployment of security resources to enhance operational efficiency. More secure trains, stations, and yards. A safer LIRR","payload":{"claim_text":"What This Means for Customers and Employees: Coordinated, consistent incident handling. Intelligent deployment of security resources to enhance operational efficiency. More secure trains, stations, and yards. A safer LIRR."},"evidence_refs":[{"source_id":"meeting_doc_186706","evidence_id":"meeting_doc_186706#p013_c0004","source_path":"raw/sources/meeting_doc_186706/blocks.jsonl","page_number":13,"block_id":"p013_c0004","text_sha256":"sha256:bc2feb5862195ddcc0b70cfb2f803ee5e13474e9678545125b777ee68bb1033e","text_source":"raw_text","role":"claim"}]},"validation":{"state":"accepted","issues":[]}}
{"submission_id":"sub_a15495a691af2d95","run_id":"2026-06-21T20-11-51-798Z_3137823-bef50061_ingest_meeting-doc-186706","submitted_at":"2026-06-21T20:24:48.090Z","tool_args_sha256":"sha256:a15495a691af2d95614f60ff1f39c9f22e70cd33ed75cf0a57b222805129f6b4","schema_version":2,"tool_args":{"source_id":"meeting_doc_186706","observation_kind":"claim","local_observation_id":"claim_3_step_video_analysis_process","label":"LIRR 3-Step Video Analysis Process","raw_text":"1 Alert System Cameras and Access Alerts within monitored areas assists with detecting unusual activity; footage immediately reviewed. 2 Response Determination & Coordination Monitoring team utilizes playbook to determine response, and coordinates with MTAPD and Operating Departments, i.e. Stations. 3 OSCAR Tracking & Analysis Alerts logged and analyzed to refine monitoring, reduce false positives, and guide resource allocation.","payload":{"claim_text":"The LIRR 3-Step Process for video analysis: 1 Alert System - Cameras and Access Alerts within monitored areas assists with detecting unusual activity; footage immediately reviewed. 2 Response Determination & Coordination - Monitoring team utilizes playbook to determine response, and coordinates with MTAPD and Operating Departments, i.e. Stations. 3 OSCAR Tracking & Analysis - Alerts logged and analyzed to refine monitoring, reduce false positives, and guide resource allocation."},"evidence_refs":[{"source_id":"meeting_doc_186706","evidence_id":"meeting_doc_186706#p009_c0003","source_path":"raw/sources/meeting_doc_186706/blocks.jsonl","page_number":9,"block_id":"p009_c0003","text_sha256":"sha256:9b73b37dd04050f4f3bd916b0249480c4d45c0985a1fa788630478e10d18a552","text_source":"raw_text","role":"claim"}]},"validation":{"state":"accepted","issues":[]}}
